'''二硫化铀'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为US<sub>2</sub>。它可由[[二氧化铀|二氧化铀]]或[[八氧化三铀|八氧化三铀]]和[[硼|硼]]与[[硫|硫]]的混合物在800 °C反应制得。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Breton|first1=Logan S.|last2=Klepov|first2=Vladislav V.|last3=zur Loye|first3=Hans-Conrad|title=Facile Oxide to Chalcogenide Conversion for Actinides Using the Boron–Chalcogen Mixture Method|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=142|issue=33|year=2020|pages=14365–14373|issn=0002-7863|doi=10.1021/jacs.0c06483}}</ref>它在高温下可以被氧气氧化为八氧化三铀、[[硫酸铀酰|硫酸铀酰]]和其它铀的氧化物或硫氧化物。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Nuclear Materials|volume=50|issue=2|language=en|date=1974-03|pages=200–206|doi=10.1016/0022-3115(74)90156-1|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0022311574901561|title=Interaction between uranium sulphides and oxygen|accessdate=2020-08-21|author=M. Paljević, Z. Ban, Z. Despotović, L. Omejec|archive-date=2018-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180608064531/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/0022311574901561|dead-url=no}}</ref>它和金属、硫反应，或和金属的硫化物反应，可以得到RhUS<sub>3</sub><ref>{{cite journal|journal=Inorganica Chimica Acta|volume=140|language=en|date=1987-12|pages=93–95|doi=10.1016/S0020-1693(00)81057-9|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0020169300810579|title=Synthesis, crystal structure and magnetic properties of new ternary uranium chalcogenides: RuUS3 and RhUS3|accessdate=2020-08-21|author=A. Daoudi, H. Noel|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120091133/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0020169300810579|dead-url=no}}</ref>、Ba<sub>2</sub>Cu<sub>2</sub>US<sub>5</sub><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Zeng|first1=Hui-yi|last2=Yao|first2=Jiyong|last3=Ibers|first3=James A.|title=Synthesis, structure, and magnetic properties of Ba2Cu2US5|journal=Journal of Solid State Chemistry|volume=181|issue=3|year=2008|pages=552–555|issn=00224596|doi=10.1016/j.jssc.2007.12.025}}</ref>等化合物。

